              <span class="text-gray-700">PageSpeed 95+ for SEO is critical</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" class="mt-1.5 w-5 h-5 text-orange-600 rounded border-gray-300 focus:ring-orange-500" checked readonly>
              <span class="text-gray-700">You want to launch in 2-3 days with stunning results</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-gray-300 p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-700 mb-4">Choose Webflow If:</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" class="mt-1.5 w-5 h-5 text-gray-600 rounded border-gray-300 focus:ring-gray-500" checked readonly>
              <span class="text-gray-700">You're a larger architecture firm with 20+ projects</span>
